		<div class="comment-author vcard">
		<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/2733ae3c51e750254c4e2bde4bb8d48a?s=52&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cannabisnews.org%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fcomfy%2Fstyles%2Fdefault%2Fimg%2Fdefault_avatar.png%3Fs%3D52&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-52 photo' height='52' width='52' />		<cite class="fn">David</cite>
