		<p>What a JOKE. The author of this article simply forgot to mention that there have been over 5,000 years of human trials regarding consumption via smoking weed…with no deaths or cancer or even proof that any damage to the lungs exists.<br />
What a JOKE. The author listed every AMERICAN society that makes decisions on Marijuana&#8217;s health effects…meanwhile Spain just made Marijuana #3 on its &#8216;Most effective against Cancer&#8217; list.<br />
Unfortunately, this author wants you to think that America has cornered the market on intelligence surrounding Weed.<br />
What a JOKE.</p>
		
		
		<div class="reply">
		<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/pot-more-dangerous-than-you-know/2013/06/18/?replytocom=22568#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-22568", "22568", "respond", "938")'>Reply</a>		</div>

